{
  "texts": [
    "In order to utilize thematically augmented characteristics for breast tumor separation, this research suggests a brand-new deep-feature integrated level set block.",
    "Net-based model is initially trained to retrieve various characteristics at various phases.",
    "Every level depicts distinct aspects differently.",
    "Furthermore, at the conclusion of every phase, an unique level-set mechanism is added to acquire better detailed and realistic feature maps.",
    "In the performance component of the level-set technique, a novel feature-discriminator is developed to improve the low confidence values at the borders."
  ]
}